9:\"With the release of wpStoreCart 2.2.9, you can now have wpStoreCart automatically issue serial numbers when a product is purchased. That means if you sell your own software, or you have purchased the resale rights to other&#8217;s software, you can now use wpStoreCart to not only sell the software, but to automatically issue a serial&#8230; <a class=\"continue_reading\" href=\"http://wpstorecart.com/sell-software-with-serial-numbers-using-wordpress/\">Continue reading &#187;</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"admin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1755:\"<p>With the release of wpStoreCart 2.2.9, you can now have wpStoreCart automatically issue serial numbers when a product is purchased.  That means if you sell your own software, or you have purchased the resale rights to other&#8217;s software, you can now use wpStoreCart to not only sell the software, but to automatically issue a serial number.  This is perfect for software developers and resellers who want to leverage a WordPress ecommerce solution with a minimal amount of work.<br />\n<span id=\"more-658\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL.png\"><img src=\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"SERIAL\" width=\"648\" height=\"302\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-659\" /></a></p>\n<p>Use the <strong>Edit Products > Downloads</strong> tab to add serial numbers, as seen in the screenshot above.</p>\n<p>Also included in 2.2.9, is the ability to specify an Orders &#038; Downloads page in General Settings.  This will allow the [downloadurl] in emails and other wpStoreCart functions to know where to tell your users to browse to.</p>\n<p>Speaking of serial numbers and emails, there was a new email added: Email Sent When Issuing Serial Number</p>\n<p>Some of the other changes in 2.2.9 are:<br />\n- Fixed a bug that had caused the emails that were to be sent after an order is approved to fail<br />\n- Added a new tab for product editing: downloads<br />\n- Fixed a bug that caused PayPal donations to be activated when they should not be<br />\n- Added the echoFields() method to the PaymentGateway() class for debugging problems in the payment gateway<br />\n- Started adding a new mode to the cart that uses Cookies instead of Sessions to store the carts contents</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"http://wpstorecart.com/sell-software-with-serial-numbers-using-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"url\";s:68:\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL-150x150.png\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"\n			\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:60:\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/SERIAL.png\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:5:\"tit