Press theme, that will be included for free with wpStoreCart 2.1.9 and above and is also available as a separate download.  The theme requires wpStoreCart 2.1.9 or higher, and includes a fully configurable slideshow, product previews, dynamic font replacement of the header with 5 included fonts, widget support, and much more.</p>\n<p><center><a href=\"http://wpstorecart.com/demo/\"><img src=\"http://wpstorecart.com/demo/wp-content/themes/wpStoreCartTheme/screenshot.png\" alt=\"wpStoreCartTheme\" /></a></center><br />\n<span id=\"more-500\"></span><br />\nYou can play with a pre-release live demo of wpStoreCartTheme here:<br />\n<a href=\"http://wpstorecart.com/demo/\">http://wpstorecart.com/demo/</a></p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s a screenshot of the administration for the theme:<br />\n<center><a href=\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/options.png\"><img src=\"http://wpstorecart.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/options-300x211.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"options\" width=\"300\" height=\"211\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-501\" /></a></center></p>\n<p>Let us know what you think!  We&#8217;re still working on product pages and blog pages, but we&#8217;re near the end of development.  Expect the theme as well as wpStoreCart 2.1.9 to be released <del datetime=\"2011-04-02T09:04:58+00:00\">within the next 2 weeks</del> as soon as it&#8217;s done.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"http://wpstorecart.com/a-new-free-premium-ecommerce-wordpress-template-wpstorecarttheme/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang