INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2011-05-11 03:10:17','2011-05-11 03:10:17','CLiCKPLAYceu and Cosine Health Strategies was created because we like people and we want everyone to be as healthy as possible. We don\'t just push our tofu agendas- we actually are real health care professionals. Donn Kropp founded the company in 2009 out of a desire to bring others to greater levels of health and wellness. With over ten years of emergency and trauma room experience Donn brings a seasoned, yet fresh approach. We also inject a healthy dose of fun and humor into our business and products. Enough about us, we want our business to be about you! We want you to learn and have fun while you are doing it so that you can give the people you serve the highest quality care possible.\r\n\r\nAbout Our Founder/Executive Director/Instructor, Donn Kropp:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://clickplayceu.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/kropp_donn-about.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-199 alignleft\" title=\"Donn Kropp, Founder of Cogent CEUs\" src=\"http://clickplayceu.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/kropp_donn-about.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"175\" height=\"183\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Academic Stuff:</strong> Bachelors of Science in Nursing 2001 from University of North Carolina- Charlotte\r\n\r\n<strong>Work Experience Stuff:</strong> ER/Trauma Nurse, Medical Consultant\r\n\r\n<strong>Stuff He Likes to Do:</strong> Travel, read, anything death defying, golf, exercise, eat\r\n\r\n<strong>Places He\'s Lived:</strong> Japan, North Carolina, California\r\n\r\n<strong>Places He\'s Visited:</strong> Japan, Saipan, Belize, Ecuador, Costa Rica, Korea, India, Haiti, Germany, Czech Republic, Austria, Mexico\r\n\r\n<strong>Places He Wants To Visit:</strong> New Zealand, Australia, Iceland, Kansas\r\n\r\n<strong>Embarrassing Moment:  </strong>\"About thirty seconds before giving a speech I spilled water in my lap from a water bottle. There was no podium to hide behind so I just started the speech out by saying I was just diagnosed with early onset urinary incontinence. It took about ten minutes to dry and it was quite embarrassing. Note to self- no water before giving a speech.\"\r\n\r\n<strong>If you had a robot what would you train it to do?</strong> Give me daily deep tissue shiatsu massages.','About','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2012-01-28 12:36:38','2012-01-28 20:36:38','',0,'http://wordpress.dev/clients/cogentceus/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(261,1,'2011-11-28 10:03:22','2011-11-28 18:03:22','Cogent Health Strategies was created because we like people and we want everyone to be as healthy as possible. We don\'t just push our tofu agendas- we actually are real health care professionals. Donn Kropp founded the company in 2009 out of a desire to bring others to greater levels of health and wellness. With over ten years of emergency and trauma room experience Donn brings a seasoned, yet fresh approach.Â Cogent means to make something lucid, coherent and easily understandable-We also inject a healthy dose of fun and humor into our business and products. Enough about us, we want our business to be about you! We want you to learn and have fun while you are doing it so that you can give the people you service the highest quality care possible.\r\n\r\nAbout Our Founder/Executive Director/Instructor:\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-199 alignleft\" title=\"Donn Kropp, Founder of Cogent CEUs\" src=\"http://clickplayceu.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/kropp_donn-about.jpg\" alt=\"Donn Kropp, Founder of Cogent CEUs\" width=\"175\" height=\"183\" />\r\n\r\nDonn Kropp\r\n\r\nAcademic Stuff: Bachelors of Science in Nursing 2001 from University of North Carolina- Charlotte\r\n\r\nWork Experience Stuff: ER/Trauma Nurse, Medical Consultant\r\n\r\nStuff He Likes to Do: Travel, read, anything death defying, golf, exercise, eat\r\n\r\nPlaces He\'s Lived: Japan, North Carolina, California\r\n\r\nPlaces He\'s Visited: Japan, Saipan, Belize, Ecuador, Costa Rica, Korea,