ial relationships. Our lawyers make us say this.','Respiratory System Part 2: Asthma, Pneumonia, COPD','Millions of Americans suffer from asthma, pneumonia and COPD. These common respiratory diseases are frequently talked about but poorly understood. It only takes seconds for one of these diseases to claim its victim. Our instructor, Donn Kropp, RN, BSN, uncovers the mysteries surrounding these ailments. Do you have the knowledge to help those who suffer from asthma, pneumonia and COPD?  ','publish','closed','closed','','respiratory-system-part-2-asthma-pneumonia-copd','','','2011-12-07 10:44:41','2011-12-07 18:44:41','',0,'http://clickplayceu.com/?p=176',3,'post','',0),(265,1,'2011-11-28 10:11:50','2011-11-28 18:11:50','This is part two of the series on the respiratory system. This course will be building off the knowledge already gained in part one, \"Respiratory System: The Foundation\" Millions of Americans suffer from asthma, pneumonia and COPD. These common respiratory diseases are frequently talked about but poorly understood. It only takes seconds for one of these diseases to claim its victim. Our instructor, Donn Kropp, RN, BSN, uncovers the mysteries surrounding these ailments. Do you have the knowledge to help those who suffer from asthma, pneumonia and COPD?','Respiratory System Part 2: Asthma, Pneumonia, COPD','Millions of Americans suffer from asthma, pneumonia and COPD. These common respiratory diseases are frequently talked about but poorly understood. It only takes seconds for one of these diseases to claim its victim. Our instructor, Donn Kropp, RN, BSN, uncovers the mysteries surrounding these ailments. Do you have the knowledge to help those who suffer from asthma, pneumonia and COPD?  ','inherit','closed','closed','','176-revision-4','','','2011-11-28 10:11:50','2011-11-28 18:11:50','',176,'http://clickplayceu.com/2011/11/176-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(266,1,'2011-08-23 05:15:07','2011-08-23 05:15:07','It only takes seconds for a respirato